5|$|After {{maintaining}} an informal public distance for eight years, Bill Clinton and Gore reunited {{for the media}} in August 2009 after Clinton arranged {{for the release of}} two journalists who were being <b>held</b> <b>hostage</b> in North Korea. The two women were employees of Gore's Current TV.|$|E
